(335, 'notifier-cache', '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>\n<notifier>\n	<latest>2.5</latest>\n	<changelog>		\n<![CDATA[\n<div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;">\n\n<h3>Version 2.5 - July 29, 2013</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Improved: WPML compatibility with the plugins latest version</li>\n<li>Fixed: Heights of content images issue on mobile devices</li>\n<li>Updated: Slider Revolution Plugin version updated ( v 3.0.5 )</li>\n<li>Improved: Compatibility with gravity forms plugin</li>\n<li>Improved: Resize image function improved</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Version 2.4 - May 11, 2013</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: OrderBy paramater to product shortcode </li>\n<li>Updated: New version of Slider Revolution plugin included.</li>\n<li>Improved: WooCommerce product image galleries</li>\n<li>Improved: PHP 5.3 compatibility </li>\n<li>Improved: Photo gallery shortcode layout</li>\n<li>Improved: Video embed function</li>\n<li>Fixed: Product image variations issue of WooCommerce</li>\n<li>Fixed: IE9 button style issue fixed when WooCommerce plugin active</li>\n<li>Fixed: Button link edit issue fixed on editor. </li>\n<li>Fixed: Blog module pagination bug fixed</li>\n<li>Fixed: Odd looking overlay icon on images of single portfolio page when used a small portfolio image</li>\n<li>Fixed: Poster image size issues of  self-hosted audio and video</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<h3>Version 2.3 - March 23, 2013</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Product comments</li>\n<li>Fixed: Code box module column widths fixed when padding is off  </li>\n<li>Fixed: Revolution slider css issues fixed when non-responsive mode is ON</li>\n<li>Fixed: Minor bug fixes</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Version 2.2 - March 15, 2013</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: HTML validation issue that started with v.2.1</li>\n<li>Fixed: Default font-face and link issue for Revolution Slider</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Version 2.1 - March 12, 2013</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Revolution Slider</li>\n<li>Added: WooCommerce 2.0.2 compatibility</li>\n<li>Fixed: Image resizing issue of WPMU (multisite) with WordPress 3.5.1</li>\n<li>Fixed: Product ajax pagination issue </li>\n<li>Improved: CSS files </li>\n<li>Added:  WPML translation option added for map url field where in the contact module</li>\n<li>Fixed: WPML Product category name translation issue. </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Version 2.0 - February 15, 2013</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Ability to add document names to the attached documents of products</li>\n<li>Added: Ability to use URL''s for Email icon in social media options</li>\n<li>Added: Link target option added on custom links for home page contents</li>\n<li>Improved: RTL support </li>\n<li>Improved: Password protected product and portfolio posts</li>\n<li>Improved: .po file improved</li>\n<li>Improved: Header options with WooCommerce </li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: WPML related bug fixes</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Fixed bug on filterable portfolio galleries when custom categories selected via template builder.</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Hide big dates option bug on single pages</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Lowercase highlighted terms bug on search result. </li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Showing product name bug when WooCommerce category listing option active</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Sidebar misplacement issue fixed when a portfolio or product category is empty</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v2.0</h5>\n[please update all files]\n\n\n<h3>THEME UPDATED: Version 1.9 - January 18, 2013</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>New Option: New blog option added into the Blog Options that lets you control the length of the blog texts on listing pages.</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Duplicated row id bug fixed.</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Codebox module transparency bug fixed.</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Space bug fixed in the subject line of the contact form submissions</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Pagination bug fixed on blog categories</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Search icon color fixed for Rose skin.</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Fixed broken page problem on Portfolio and Product categories when WPML plugin is active. </li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Fixed blank page issue of some plugins settings page on the admin part.</li>\n<li>Improved: Social media icon heights fixed.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.9</h5>\n[please update all files]\n\n<h3>Version 1.8 - December 16, 2012</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Portfolio filter bug fixed.</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Image align centre bug fixed.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.8</h5>\n/portfolio_loop.php\n/css/style.css\n/style.css\n\n\n\n<h3>Version 1.7 - December 13, 2012</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Improvements & fixes for WordPress 3.5</li>\n<li>Improved WPML support</li>\n<li>Added new sidebar location for archives and tags</li>\n<li>Improved single portfolio pages for better plugin compatibility </li>\n<li>Improved WooCommerce support</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.7</h5>\n/content_generator.php\n/rt-framework/admin/js/script.js\n/rt-framework/classes/page_layout_options.php\n/rt-framework/classes/sidebar_creator.php\n/rt-framework/functions/theme_functions.php\n/rt-framework/functions/rt_shortcodes.php\nfunctions.php\nsingle-portfolio.php\npost_content.php\nstyle.css\n\n\n<h3>Version 1.6 - October 10, 2012</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: New Slider  - Nivo Slider</li>  \n<li>Added: Video support for Flex Slider</li>  \n<li>Added: New post type "Aside" added to posts</li> \n<li>Added: Portfolio categories option to Sidebar Creator </li>   \n<li>Improved: WooCommerce support</li>  \n<li>Improved: According and Tab shortcodes improved</li>  \n<li>Improved: Code improvements</li>  \n<li>Bug fixed: Excerpt bug fixed</li>  \n<li>Bug fixed: Home page sidebar </li>  \n<li>Bug fixed: Custom styling bug fixed on home page contents</li>  \n<li>Bug fixed: Slider shortcode bug fixed</li>  \n<li>Bug Fixed: Bug fixed on Safari browsers when some extensions are active</li>  \n<li>Updated: .po/.mo files</li>  \n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.6</h5>\n[please update all files]\n\n<h4>Version 1.5 - September 15, 2012</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Bug fixed: Don''t show product descriptions bug fixed for Products widget</li>\n<li>Improved: Margins improved for product shortcode and widget</li>\n<li>Bug fixed: Self-hosted videos bug on blog and portfolio</li>\n<li>Css improvements & menu over breadcrumb issue fixed</li>\n<li>Improved: comment form</li>\n<li>Improved: css files</li>\n<li>Improved: WP Menus, now users are able to change the menu names or assign their existing menus to the menu locations</li>\n<li>Improved: Code improvements</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.5</h5>\n[please update all files]\n\n\n\n<h4>Version 1.4 – August 28, 2012</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: New widget for products.</li>\n<li>Added: New shortcode for products. </li>\n<li>Improved: Fancy box plugin compatibility with built in jQuery functions</li>\n<li>Improved: Portfolio and Product thumbnail resize function</li>\n<li>Improved: Drop down menu improved for android devices</li>\n<li>Improved: Paddings for user added layouts via quick styling.</li>\n<li>Improved: Post archive pages, now displays tag and category descriptions </li>\n<li>Improved: Logo position for mobile devices</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Self hosted video and audio bug on single portfolio pages</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Search icon color bug fixed when using custom colors and other skins</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Footer positioning script removed to solve incompatibility issue with sliders</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Duplicating product content bug fixed when WooCommerce & WPML are active at the same time.</li>\n<li>Bug Fixed: Cutting text issue fixed on tabs shortcode. </li>\n<li>Bug fixed: Date color bug fixed when using custom colors and other skins on mobile devices</li>\n<li>Updated: German translation file</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.4</h5>\n(- archive.php, \n- portfolio_loop.php, \n- product_loop.php, \n- single-portfolio.php, \n- custom-styling.php, \n - /css/[all-files], \n- /js/script.js, \n- /rt-framework/[all files] ,\n- editor-style.css ) \n\n\n\n<h4>Version 1.3 – August 19, 2012</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Filterable portfolio gallery option (Portfolio Posts module of template builder as Filter Navigation)</li>\n<li>Added: Transition Effect and Thumbnail Pager, Heading Pager  options added to Slider Module of  Template Builder</li>\n<li>Added: Self hosted Video and Audio formats for Blog</li>\n<li>Added: Self hosted Video and Audio formats for Portfolio</li>\n<li>Added: Change box background color option for the home page contents. </li>\n<li>Added: Static sidebar position for footer widgets (activate first via Footer Options)</li>\n<li>Added: German translation by Uwe Schmidt – www.vitaloage.com</li>\n<li>Added: Open in new tab option added to Photo Gallery Shortcode</li>\n<li>Added: Crop image option added for the portfolio images</li>\n<li>Added: Open/Close Responsive Design feature added in General Options</li>\n<li>Added: External link and Open in new Tab features added for portfolio items</li>\n<li>Improvement: Now slider images are also clickable in the main slider.</li>\n<li>Improvement: Product showcase improved</li>\n<li>Improvement: Several improvements for plugin compatibility </li>\n<li>Improvement: WooCommerce view sub categories mode and styles</li>\n<li>Fixed: Editor bug fixed on portfolio and product pages in the admin panel </li>\n<li>Fixed: Header bug fixed that effects IE users when text field used but header image is empty.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.3</h5>\n[please update all files]\n\n\n<h4>Version 1.2 – August 07, 2012</h4>\n<ul>\n\n<li>Added: WooCommerce 1.6.1 Support! Create your shop with unique RT-Theme 17 style and layout options. </li> \n<li> Added: New module, "Code Box" added for Template Builder. Now you are able to use your own HTML codes and shortcodes within a module.  </li> \n<li> Added: Unique ID numbers for each row. Now you can create a CSS Rule for each row in your templates. </li> \n<li> Added: New sidebar position for search results </li> \n<li> Added:  Ability to use any page as home page with custom template (via Settings->Reading Settings -> A static page ) </li> \n<li> Added: New documents into the Setup Assistant  </li> \n<li> Improved: Discus plugin compatibility </li> \n<li> Improved: Compatibility warnings </li> \n<li> Improved: 404 Page </li> \n<li> Bug fixed: Styling fixes for issue when using header images for home page and fixed display issue on archive pages. </li> \n<li> Bug fixed: Spacing issue when a product category has category description </li> \n<li> Bug fixed: Menu color bug fixed that affects menu items when Cufon font selected </li> \n<li> Bug fixed: minor bug fixed that effects php 5.4 users. </li> \n<li> Updated: .po /.mo files </li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.2</h5>\n[please update all files]\n\n\n<h4>Version 1.1 - July 27, 2012</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New Feature: Added free code spaces for before &lt;/head&gt;  and  before &lt;/body&gt; into the General Options</li>\n<li>New Feature: Ability to use social media icons top of the page, footer or elsewhere with a  shortcode</li>\n<li>New Feature: Added new options to hide/show categories, big dates, small dates, author names, comment numbers into the Blog Options</li>\n<li>Improved: PrettyPhoto modified for better performance on mobile screens</li>\n<li>Bug fixed:  bug fixed on the header image positions when breadcrumb and search is OFF</li>\n<li>Bug fixed: align bug fixed on auto thumbnail shortcode when  frame = false</li>\n<li>Bug fixed: Overlaying issue on the long drop-down menus</li>\n<li>Bug fixed: wrong dates bug fixed on single blog pages</li>\n</ul>\n	\n<h5>Affected Files - v1.1</h5>\n- /css/style.css<br />\n- /css/prettyPhoto.css<br />\n- /css/rt-css-framework.css<br />\n- /rt-framework/functions/rt_shortcodes.php<br />\n- /rt-framework/admin/options/rt_general_options.php<br />\n- /rt-framework/admin/options/rt_blog_options.php<br />\n- /rt-framework/admin/options/rt_social_options.php<br />\n- /js/scripts.js<br />\n- sub_page_header.php<br />\n- post_content.php<br />\n- footer.php<br />\n- loop.php<br />\n- header.php<br />\n\n\n<h4>Version 1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial theme version.</li> \n</ul>\n</div>\n]]>\n	</changelog>\n</notifier>', 'yes'),
