(1, 1, '2013-07-15 17:37:43', '2013-07-15 17:37:43', '<span style="text-align: justify; display: block;"><a href="FaithFarmCorporate/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/faith_farm_bridge.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1790 alignright" alt="faith_farm_bridge" src="FaithFarmCorporate/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/faith_farm_bridge-300x226.png" width="300" height="226" /></a>We are happy to announce that the bridge renovation project at our Boynton Beach location is underway. Thanks to the generous support of many we are now able to begin this project. Our bridge is the only ingress/egress for campus traffic: Faith Farm''s Thrift Store, Customers, Staff and Program Residents, Faith Farm trucks picking up or making deliveries and vendors. The property is surrounded by canals on all sides. Deterioration of the bridge is occurring on a constant basis due to it''s age, volume of traffic and increased loads. Recent X-rays of the bridge show that existing joists do not have the steel reinforcements to support the truck traffic at the current span. Structural Engineers have approved a twelve month usage span structural bracing with crutch bents (steel supports) under the bridge which will maintain the safety of the bridge. The Boynton Beach Thrift Store provides 60% of the organization''s funds supporting the Men''s and Women''s free recovery program as well as the location for the Ministry Administrative Office, Celebrate Recovery and a Polling facility. No Capital funds are available but a new bridge must be built at a cost of $1,140,000. All funds raised will be allocated to "Save Our Bridge" without any offset for fundraising or administrative fees.</span>', 'Boynton Beach Bridge Project Underway!!!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2013-07-25 20:48:18', '2013-07-25 20:48:18', '', 0, 'FaithFarmCorporate/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(2, 1, '2013-07-15 17:37:43', '2013-07-15 17:37:43', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="FaithFarmCorporate/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sample-page', '', '', '2013-07-15 17:37:43', '2013-07-15 17:37:43', '', 0, 'FaithFarmCorporate/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
