(1752, 1, '2013-07-19 17:49:11', '2013-07-19 17:49:11', 'We are happy to announce that the bridge renovation project at our Boynton Beach location is underway. Thanks to the generous support of many we are now able to begin this project. For those who are oblivious to the reasons for the new bridge, please see below -\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: small;">Our bridge is the </span><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow;">only ingress/egress </span></span><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow;">for campus traffic: Faith Farm''s Thrift Store, Customers, Staff and Program Residents, Faith Farm trucks picking up or making deliveries and vendors. </span></span><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: small;">The property is surrounded by canals on all sides.</span> </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: small;">Deterioration </span><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: small;">of the bridge is occurring on a constant basis due to it''s age, volume of traffic and increased loads.</span> </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: small;">Recent X-rays of the bridge </span><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: small;">show that existing joists do not have the steel reinforcements to support the truck traffic at the current span.</span> </span></span></li>\r\n	<li>Structural Engineers have approved a twelve month usage span structural bracing with crutch bents (steel supports) under the bridge which will maintain the safety of the bridge.</li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: small;">The <b><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow;">Boynton Beach Thrift Store provides 60% of the organization''s funds </span></span></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: small;">supporting the Men''s and Women''s free recovery program as well as the location for the Ministry Administrative Office, Celebrate Recovery and a Polling facility.</span> </span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: small;">No Capital funds <span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow;">are available but a new bridge must be built at a cost of $1,140,000. All funds raised will be allocated to </span></span><b><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow;">"Save Our Bridge" </span></span></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Arial,Arial Narrow; font-size: large;"><span style="font-size: small;">without any offset for fundraising or administrative fees.</span> </span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Boynton Beach Bridge Project Underway!!!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-3', '', '', '2013-07-19 17:49:11', '2013-07-19 17:49:11', '', 1, 'FaithFarmCorporate/?p=1752', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
